    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>Installation</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
            <title>Fuel Injector Assemblies</title>
            <figure id="f3350007197" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figk11/K11023.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="152px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Fuel Injector assembly</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Upper O-ring</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Lower O-ring</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Nozzle gasket</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel nozzle</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel inlet port</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <specpara>
                <caution>
                    <para>To prevent engine damage, replace upper and lower injector O-rings and nozzle gasket each time
                        an injector is removed.
                    </para>
                </caution>
            </specpara>
            <step1>
                <para id="s0716" count="1">Lubricate new injector upper O-ring with clean engine oil and slide in the
                    recess just above the fuel inlet ports.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Lubricate new lower O-ring with clean engine oil and slide in the recess just below the
                    fuel inlet ports.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f3350007196" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figh11/H11041.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Injector nozzle gasket</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Injector nozzle gasket</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Injector nozzle</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <specpara>
                <caution>
                    <para>To prevent engine damage, do not nick or scratch injector nozzle gasket.</para>
                </caution>
            </specpara>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Push a new injector nozzle gasket on injector nozzle using a deep socket to support the
                    nozzle gasket. Nozzle gasket can go on either way.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f3350007207" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figk11/K11026.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Injector assembly installation</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Injector hold down clamp notch</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Oil inlet O-ring (high-pressure)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Injector assembly slot</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Align each injector assembly slot with hold down clamp notch and install assembly in
                    cylinder head.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <specpara>
                <caution>
                    <para>To prevent engine damage, do not use air tools to install fuel injectors.</para>
                </caution>
            </specpara>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Tighten injector hold down clamp bolts using a T40 Torx bit (
                    <hotlnk document="eges3351_191.xml" xrefid="t335000703" appearance="hottext">Fuel Injector Remover
                        Tool</hotlnk>)
                    <xref refid="t335000703"/>.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Tighten six injector hold down clamp bolts to
                    <hotlnk document="eges3351_190.xml" xrefid="t335000702" appearance="hottext">special torque</hotlnk>
                    <xref refid="t335000702"/>. Injector will be placed at the correct depth.
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
